sellerAgent.name: Shelly Stuhr - 253 Realty - Your Home Sold Guaranteed Or I Will Buy It

data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3bd 2ba house. Natural light shines in the main living area that is adorned w/coved ceilings & arched doorways. Cozy up to the wood fireplace & enjoy how quiet & peaceful the inside is. Main level has hardwood floors, a spacious kitchen w/eating nook, 2 bds & 1 full bath. Lower level has a spacious living area, large bedroom w/walk in closet, full bath, flex space & separate entrance! Great for an investment; LTR, Airbnb or house hack opportunity. Sewer line was replaced, has updated wiring & plumbing, newer H2O heater. Back yard is fully-fenced, has alley access, detached garage & shed. Plenty of parking space, amazingly located 5 min from freeway, close to shopping & Lincoln District. Turn-key & Pre-inspected
